User functions

Partition of a collection of bipartite networks based on their common mesoscale structures

extract_nodes_groups()
Extract nodes groups from a fitSimpleSBMPop, fitBipartiteSBMPop, bmpop or bisbmpop object

colSBM R6 class objects

bmpop
An R6 Class object, a collection of model for population of sbm netowrks
fitSimpleSBMPop
An R6 Class object, a fitted population of netowrks sbm once $optimize() is done
bisbmpop
An R6 Class object, a collection of model for population of BiSBM networks
fitBipartiteSBMPop
An R6 Class object, a fitted population of netowrks sbm once $optimize() is done

Plot matrix summaries of the collection mesoscale structure
plot(<bisbmpop>)
Plot the state-space exploration plot for a bipartite collection object
